# SecureAI MicroShield — Trivy Ignore List
# Only unfixable OS-level CVEs are listed here. All application-level CVEs must be fixed.
# Reviewed: 2026-04-07

# linux-libc-dev: Kernel header CVEs — not exploitable in containerized workloads.
# These have no upstream fix and are flagged against the development headers package,
# not the running kernel. Containers share the host kernel and cannot be patched here.
CVE-2013-7445
CVE-2019-19449
CVE-2019-19814
CVE-2021-3847
CVE-2021-3864

# ncurses: Buffer overflow in terminal handling — not reachable in headless containers.
CVE-2025-69720
